OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FHeavy rain clearing to the
OL,6,Feast in the morning to leave a largely
OL,7,Fdry day with some bright spells and
OL,8,Fjust the odd isolated shower. Light
OL,9,Fwinds strengthening in evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fwith heavy outbreaks of rain Sunday.
OL,13,FSunny spells and a few showers on
OL,14,FMonday. Dry with sunny spells Tuesday.
OL,15,FStrong winds and risk of gales Sunday,
OL,16,Fthen becoming light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
